  "body": "Currently `eth_estimateGas` is defined here with only the [transaction param](https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/main/src/eth/execute.json#L26). In legacy RPC API spec, the specification of a block number or tag was required:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20375610/139799271-a403bcf0-9186-44f8-a677-0024213fd76e.png)\r\n\r\nAnd for additional context, here are the parameters defined for `eth_call`:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20375610/139799132-db9e64be-0f53-4e0e-ad36-6888d08e1f1b.png)",
